sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuthProxy as oauth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant OAuthServer as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DashboardApp as odh-dashboard<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NotebookCtrl as odh-notebook-controller<br/>8081/TCP HTTP
    participant KFNotebookCtrl as kf-notebook-controller
    participant ModelMeshCtrl as ModelMesh Controller<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelMeshPod as ModelMesh Runtime Pod<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Client as Inference Client

    Note over User, DashboardApp: Flow 1: User Accesses RHOAI Dashboard

    User->>Router: GET /dashboard<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Router->>OAuthProxy: Forward<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS (reencrypt)
    OAuthProxy->>OAuthServer: OAuth2 Auth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>OAuth Client Credentials
    OAuthServer-->>OAuthProxy: Auth Token
    OAuthProxy->>DashboardApp: Forward Request<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (localhost)<br/>Bearer Token (pass-access-token)
    DashboardApp->>K8sAPI: API Calls<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>DashboardApp: API Response
    DashboardApp-->>OAuthProxy: HTML Response
    OAuthProxy-->>Router: HTTPS Response
    Router-->>User: Dashboard UI

    Note over User, KFNotebookCtrl: Flow 3: Notebook Creation

    User->>DashboardApp: Create Notebook
    DashboardApp->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>KFNotebookCtrl: Watch Event
    KFNotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create StatefulSet<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>NotebookCtrl: Watch Event
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Route + oauth-proxy<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    User->>Router: Access Notebook<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>OpenShift OAuth

    Note over Client, ModelMeshPod: Flow 2: Model Inference via ModelMesh

    Client->>ModelMeshPod: Inference Request<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>plaintext (NetworkPolicy)
    ModelMeshPod->>ModelMeshCtrl: Internal Communication<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>plaintext (internal mesh)
    ModelMeshCtrl->>K8sAPI: API Access<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>ModelMeshCtrl: Response
    ModelMeshCtrl-->>ModelMeshPod: Response
    ModelMeshPod-->>Client: Inference Result
